{{ $json.html_url }}

Facility: {{ $('Build facility files').item.json.facility.name }}
County: {{ $('Build facility files').item.json.facility.county }}
Note: {{ $('Build facility files').item.json.facility.note }}

Merge the PR to publish the pin on the /locations map.

=A data center was found but its county ({{ $json.missingCounty }}) isn't in the centroid lookup, so it has no map coordinates yet.

Facility: {{ $json.facility.name }}
Note: {{ $json.facility.note }}

To place it: add "{{ $json.missingCounty }}" (lowercased) with [lat, lng] to pipeline/texas-county-centroids.json, then it'll be picked up next run.
